00082 
00083 /* 
00084  * #define GSM_MULT_R(a, b) (* word a, word b, !(a == b == MIN_WORD) *) \
00085  *  (0x0FFFF & SASR(((longword)(a) * (longword)(b) + 16384), 15))
00086  */
00087 #define GSM_MULT_R(a, b) /* word a, word b, !(a == b == MIN_WORD) */    \
00088     (SASR( ((longword)(a) * (longword)(b) + 16384), 15 ))
00089 
00090 # define GSM_MULT(a,b)   /* word a, word b, !(a == b == MIN_WORD) */    \
00091     (SASR( ((longword)(a) * (longword)(b)), 15 ))
00092 
00093 # define GSM_L_MULT(a, b) /* word a, word b */  \
00094     (((longword)(a) * (longword)(b)) << 1)
00095 
00096 # define GSM_L_ADD(a, b)    \
00097     ( (a) <  0 ? ( (b) >= 0 ? (a) + (b) \
00098          : (utmp = (ulongword)-((a) + 1) + (ulongword)-((b) + 1)) \
00099            >= MAX_LONGWORD ? MIN_LONGWORD : -(longword)utmp-2 )   \
00100     : ((b) <= 0 ? (a) + (b)   \
00101               : (utmp = (ulongword)(a) + (ulongword)(b)) >= MAX_LONGWORD \
00102             ? MAX_LONGWORD : utmp))
00103 
00104 /*
00105  * # define GSM_ADD(a, b)   \
00106  *  ((ltmp = (longword)(a) + (longword)(b)) >= MAX_WORD \
00107  *  ? MAX_WORD : ltmp <= MIN_WORD ? MIN_WORD : ltmp)
00108  */
00109 /* Nonportable, but faster: */
00110 
00111 #define GSM_ADD(a, b)   \
00112     ((unsigned)((ltmp = (longword)(a) + (longword)(b)) - MIN_WORD) > \
00113         MAX_WORD - MIN_WORD ? (ltmp > 0 ? MAX_WORD : MIN_WORD) : ltmp)
00114 
00115 # define GSM_SUB(a, b)  \
00116     ((ltmp = (longword)(a) - (longword)(b)) >= MAX_WORD \
00117     ? MAX_WORD : ltmp <= MIN_WORD ? MIN_WORD : ltmp)
00118 
00119 # define GSM_ABS(a) ((a) < 0 ? ((a) == MIN_WORD ? MAX_WORD : -(a)) : (a))
00120

00122 
00123 # define GSM_MULT_R(a, b)   gsm_mult_r(a, b)
00124 # define GSM_MULT(a, b)     gsm_mult(a, b)
00125 # define GSM_L_MULT(a, b)   gsm_L_mult(a, b)

00127 # define GSM_L_ADD(a, b)    gsm_L_add(a, b)
